---
---

<section class="products-hero">
  <div class="products-hero-overlay"></div>

  <div class="products-hero-content">
    <h1>ØLSORTIMENT</h1>
    <p>
      Nogle specialøl skal helst reddes nu, og andre har lidt mere tid at løbe på.
      Kig efter den korte eller lange best before-dato på de forskellige produkter,
      eller sorter efter din ønskede smagstype i venstre side af menuen.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .products-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 320px;
    background-image: url("/herosocial.jpg");
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .products-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(4, 2, 2, 0.35);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .products-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    color: white;
    max-width: 900px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .products-hero-content h1 {
    margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
    font-family: "Bricolage Grotesque", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .products-hero-content p {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 750px;
    font-family: "Figtree", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 400;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .products-hero {
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    .products-hero-content {
      max-width: 560px;
      padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .products-hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .products-hero-content p {
      max-width: 500px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .products-hero {
      min-height: 280px;
    }

    .products-hero-content {
      max-width: 420px;
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .products-hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .products-hero-content p {
      max-width: 360px;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
  }
</style>